   51                   ;-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
   52                   
   53                   ;	TRANSLATE TABLE - SECTOR NUMBERS ARE TRANSLATED
   54                   ;	HERE TO DECREASE THE SYSGEN TIME FOR MISSED SECTORS
   55                   ;	WHEN SLOW CONTROLLERS ARE INVOLVED.  TRANSLATION TAKES
   56                   ;	PLACE ACCORDING TO THE "SKEW" FACTOR SET ABOVE.
   57                   
   58 0128  02          OST:	DB	NTRKS	;OPERATING SYSTEM TRACKS
   59 0129  1A          SPT:	DB	NSECTS	;SECTORS PER TRACK (CAN BE PATCHED)
'SYSGEN80 for MC CP/M Computer' 			    Z80ASM 1.32 Page   2
